# Laporan Basic Path Testing

Dokumen ini menyajikan analisis cyclomatic complexity untuk setiap modul utama dalam aplikasi Webâ€¯Cafe, sekaligus menentukan jumlah jalur uji minimum yang diperlukan.

Rumus perhitungan kompleksitas jalur:  
```text
V(G) = E âˆ’ N + 2Â·P
## ğŸ“Š Tabel Basic Path Testing

| Fungsi                  | N (Node) | E (Edge) | P | V(G)=Eâˆ’N+2Â·P | Jalur Uji Min. | Keterangan                                                      |
|-------------------------|----------|----------|---|--------------|----------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **register.php**        | 7        | 8        | 1 | 3            | 3              | 1) GET form â†’ 2) POST valid â†’ 3) POST invalid                    |
| **login.php**           | 7        | 8        | 1 | 3            | 3              | 1) GET form â†’ 2) POST success â†’ 3) POST failure                  |
| **index.php**           | 4        | 5        | 1 | 2            | 2              | 1) no session â†’ redirect; 2) session ok â†’ render konten          |
| **menu.php**            | 4        | 6        | 1 | 3            | 3              | 1) no session â†’ redirect; 2) session ok + grid; 3) session ok + tabel |
| **order.php**           | 5        | 6        | 1 | 3            | 3              | 1) GET form; 2) POST lengkap â†’ simpan; 3) POST data kurang â†’ error |
| **delete_produk.php**   | 3        | 4        | 1 | 3            | 3              | 1) id invalid; 2) id valid + success; 3) id valid + failure     |
| **logout.php**          | 2        | 2        | 1 | 1            | 1              | 1) destroy session â†’ redirect                                     |
| **profile.php**         | 6        | 7        | 1 | 2            | 2              | 1) no session â†’ redirect; 2) session ok â†’ render profile & orders |

---

## ğŸ” Rekomendasi Jalur Uji

| Fungsi                | Jalur Uji                                                                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **register.php**      | 1. GET form<br>2. POST valid<br>3. POST invalid                           |
| **login.php**         | 1. GET form<br>2. POST success<br>3. POST failure                         |
| **index.php**         | 1. Tanpa session â†’ redirect ke login<br>2. Dengan session â†’ render landing page |
| **menu.php**          | 1. Tanpa session â†’ redirect<br>2. Dengan session â†’ tampil grid menu<br>3. Dengan session â†’ tampil tabel menu |
| **order.php**         | 1. GET form order<br>2. POST lengkap â†’ simpan order<br>3. POST data kurang â†’ tampil error |
| **delete_produk.php** | 1. `id` tidak valid â†’ abort/error<br>2. `id` valid & hapus sukses â†’ redirect<br>3. `id` valid & hapus gagal â†’ abort/error |
| **logout.php**        | 1. Hancurkan session & redirect                                           |
| **profile.php**       | 1. Tanpa session â†’ redirect ke login<br>2. Dengan session â†’ fetch data & render profile & orders |
